    <question>
        <prompt>How did the Brooks-Baxter War affect Arkansas?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Led to the end of Reconstruction in Arkansas</option>
            <option letter="b">Strengthened Republican control</option>
            <option letter="c">Improved race relations</option>
            <option letter="d">Created economic prosperity</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The Brooks-Baxter War of 1874 resulted in the end of Reconstruction in Arkansas and the return of conservative Democratic control.</explanation>
